extendedInfo.description: FIATA is the international association of third party logistics (3PL) associations around the world. With 115 association members and 5,600 individual company members, FIATA is the largest non-governmental organization in the field of transportation. Its influence is worldwide. The FIATA World Congress is the premier event for the international freight forwarding community. For the first time in 30 years, the FIATA World Congress will be held in the United States.FIATA 2012 World Congress, Los Angeles, CA, October 8-12, 2012
